title: "llm-secure-cli: Unified OpenAI-Compatible CLI for AI Agents"
abstract: "A high-assurance, secure CLI for interacting with LLMs (OpenAI, OpenRouter, Ollama, LiteLLM) featuring Verifier Committee multi-LLM validation, tamper-evident audit logging with PQC signatures (ML-DSA-87 / FIPS-204), PQC encryption (ML-KEM-1024 / FIPS-203), and Zero Trust architecture for autonomous AI agent control."
